Hey Nancy, If I'm going to join you on the hypocrites couch, you may as well
join me on the "I don't know what the h*** political party to support
anymore" one!! LOL
I think I'm only Republican in that I agree with less government (not that
they truly believe that) but I lean somewhat to Libertarian (just not enough)
too.
I'm somewhere in the seeking process and at this point am too cynical to
support any political party right now. I like a LOT about the green party,
but like I said, too cynical right now. :)
sigh......and so it goes.

Ren
